description:
OfficeTeam has an excellent career opportunity for an articulate, highly-skilled Inside Sales Representative. Do you love building solid customer relationships? Then this position may be for you. 

ESSENTIAL DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES: 
	- Answer high call volume; take customer phone and web orders, respond to customer requests with accuracy and in a timely manner;
	• Follow up and respond to customers, branch and sales inquiries through project or request completion including orders, quotes, product inquiry, pricing and samples;
	• Provides outstanding customer service (phone, online and will-call clientele);
	• Provides product information as required;
	- Scheduling
	• Contacts customers for orders;
	• Demonstrate excellent written and verbal communication skills;
	• Ability to input orders, invoice and process credit cards with accuracy and attention to detail;
	• Proficient in Microsoft Office Suite and GAP software
	• Comfortable with routine administrative tasks, including paperwork and invoice processing, relaying messages, basic clerical skills; and report generation as required;
	• Highly motivated, with the ability to provide assistance in other departments as needed; and Other duties as assigned

Please email [email protected] to apply! 
 Qualifications 
	• Some College degree preferred
	• Excellent written, verbal, and interpersonal communication skills for effective interface with all internal and external contacts
	• Detail oriented with demonstrated organizational and multitasking skills a must
	• Excellent PC computer skills – Microsoft Word, Office and advanced skills in Excel
	• Team player who is assertive, goal-oriented, positive and self-motivated. High level of integrity

Please email [email protected] to apply! 
 OfficeTeam is the world's leader in professional staffing for office support jobs, focusing exclusively on the temporary and temporary-to-full-time placement of professionals in the administrative field. We are faster at finding you work because of the depth of our client network. Specifically, our professional staffing managers connect with thousands of hiring managers in North America every week to find your office support job opportunities. We evaluate all of our OfficeTeam temporaries' skills and match them with the needs of top employers in their area.

